Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Latuan Elementary School in the Municipality of Sapa-Sapa, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Imam Gayong Ligaddung Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 653
An Act Changing the Name of the Latuan Elementary School in the Municipality of Sapa-Sapa, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Imam Gayong Ligaddung Elementary School
Section 1. The Latuan Elementary School in the Municipality of Sapa-Sapa, Province of Tawi-Tawi, shall hereafter be known as the Imam Gayong Ligaddung Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
